Package org.sbml.jsbml

Interface Assignment

  • All Superinterfaces:
    java.lang.Cloneable, MathContainer, SBase, SBaseWithDerivedUnit, java.io.Serializable, javax.swing.tree.TreeNode, TreeNodeWithChangeSupport, UniqueSId
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AssignmentRule, EventAssignment, ExplicitRule, InitialAssignment, RateRule

    public interface Assignment
extends MathContainer, UniqueSId
    An Assignment can be seen as a mathematical equation with a Variable on the left hand side and an equation on the right hand side that assigns a value to the Variable.
    Since:
    0.8
    Author:
    Andreas Dräger
